cs.DL, cs.IR, cs.CY, cs.SI, cs.CR 

This paper discusses the development and analysis of impact indicators in bibliometrics, which is a topic related to digital libraries (cs.DL), information retrieval (cs.IR), cybersecurity (cs.CY), social and information networks (cs.SI), and cryptography and security (cs.CR). However, since the paper focuses more on the methodology and philosophy of research evaluation, it is less likely to belong to specific sub-categories such as cs.DB or cs.AI.
